Discover a whole new world of artistic freedom here at @Azulik Uh May. ✨ Come find us in the creative crevices of the Uh May residence and unravel the secrets of this modern paradise.

Treat your senses to the boundless tastes of @junglecuisine.azulik —a sustainable, high-end culinary experience that brings you back to the welcoming arms of Mother Nature.🍃

What are you waiting for? Book that next flight out and join us on this unforgettable adventure! 
📍 @AZULIK Uh May, Mexico

node.text:
Be one with nature at Hotel Be Tulum. 🍃 Set your heart to enjoying the verdant tropics and vibrant blues of the ocean when you stay at their one-of-a-kind villas and incredibly aesthetic suites! 🌴 Doesn't that roof deck pool look like the perfect place to get a tan? 😎

💡 BH Tip: All their accommodations are made and designed with local materials and aesthetics to truly immerse you in the Yucatan culture and the surrounding ecosystem. Choose what suits your taste, but we recommend the Oceanfront Suite and Agua Master Suite!

Is this your next destination? When was the last time you visited Mexico? 🇲🇽 

📍@betulumhotel, Tulum, Mexico

Be among the first to experience timeless glamour and modern sophistication as The Langham Jakarta finally opens its doors to welcome you with its legendary Langham service and hospitality that has won loyal patrons worldwide for 150 years. ✨

𝗢𝗻 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝘀𝘁𝗮𝘆 𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲:
1. Marvel at their ten-meter lobby with bespoke lighting and stunning interiors.
2. Indulge in culinary masterpieces at their Michelin Starred restaurants: Tom’s by Tom Aikens and T’ang Court. 😋 
3. Work remotely at The Langham Club Lounge and fuel your productivity with its amenities.
4. Have afternoon tea at Alice. 🍵 
5. Drink cocktails at Artisan, located on their rooftop, where the best views of the city and sunsets can be enjoyed.
6. End your day with a rubdown at Chuan Spa. 💆🏼‍♀️ 
7. Retire for the night in one of the 223 guest rooms all lavishly furnished and spacious to suit your taste.

Celebrate The Everday at The Langham, Jakarta. ❤️

📍 @delimakmur @langham_jakarta and @langhamhotels

Enjoying the peace and quiet with @tattivasilieva. 🛌 Located in Kaluga, Neotipi in Pine River is a destination meant to inspire you to recharge your spirits and reconnect with yourself. 🍃 

Neotipi gives you unhindered views of the surrounding nature, making your stay a truly memorable one without the usual noise and distractions. You'll be immersed in the therapeutic melodies of nature with starry nights and morning skies above your head. If you need to detach from the usual, Neotipi is where you need to be! ⛺

Are you in dire need of a vacation? Do you also like nature stays?

📸 @tattivasilieva
📍 @neotipi, Kaluga, Russia

A romantic getaway with @mariefeandjakesnow at Calilo. ❤️ With suites lavishly designed and furnished to impress, this hotel is the perfect place to create new memories and make future plans together during your stay! 😍

💡 BH Tip: The Calilo staff will be more than happy to assist you in conceptualizing and executing your romantic plans to wow your partner! From proposals to anniversaries, just share your idea and preferences and the staff will take care of it. Feel free to inquire about their couple experiences too. 💋 

When was the last time you and your loved one went on a trip together? 💖 

📸 @mariefeandjakesnow
📍 @calilo_ios, Ios, Greece
🎶 Sarah Close - Head & Heart

Catching rainbows with @reneeroaming. 🌈 At Intercontinental French Polynesia, holidays can't be ruined by a little drizzle. 🌦️

Want to maximize this dream getaway? Step off the deck of your overwater villa into the warm embrace of their tranquil lagoon. Enjoy everything from scuba diving to sunset cruises to explore their majestic reefs and discover the thriving underwater wildlife. It's a once-in-a-lifetime experience so you better book that next flight to Bora Bora!

Tell us about your favorite tropical getaway stay. 💭
